,"tid":2012551,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:52:30.000Z","msg":"其實個個國家都預期經濟短期之內難以復甦香港樓市點解反而仲會升,我個人見解係短暫反彈因為短期之內各國經濟難以復甦，而家升像係之前已經積聚到一班嘅購買力只要呢一段時間消化完呢一班購買力,如果經濟令到市民工資冇向上水平又或者甚至乎下跌嘅話,再加上而家樓價己升左5-6%之前剩餘的購買力追唔到就唔會再追住,經濟未完全復甦香港又生產唔出新一班嘅有能力嘅購買者，所以我個人見解並不需要而家這一段時間入市,因發展商已陸續推出新盤去吸收市場的購買力,所以我睇整體市場購買力好快就會被消化.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=29059534&amp;extra=page%3D1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D29059534%26extra%3Dpage%253D1&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HYgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=03eb0d86\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=29059534&amp;extra=page%3D1</a>"},{"pid":"f7db57c5fe29ff3373f32063248ea3d5c17ac504","tid":2012551,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:31:11.000Z","msg":"呢幾個星期估價升咗廿萬"},{"pid":"9c455b1cbbdf84cabaf307b457b28017c79aeb42","tid":2012551,"uid":239912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7db57c5fe29ff3373f32063248ea3d5c17ac504","tid":2012551,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:31:11.000Z","msg":"呢幾個星期估價升咗廿萬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:36:22.000Z","msg":"網上估價通常幾耐update一次？"},{"pid":"f77ad7009da5a4f673e16a9ffcde136fc9832b55","tid":2012551,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c455b1cbbdf84cabaf307b457b28017c79aeb42","tid":2012551,"uid":239912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7db57c5fe29ff3373f32063248ea3d5c17ac504","tid":2012551,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:31:11.000Z","msg":"呢幾個星期估價升咗廿萬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:36:22.000Z","msg":"網上估價通常幾耐update一次？"},"citedBy":0,"